  <brief_title>Percutaneous Nephrostomy Versus Stent In Sepsis Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>PERSIST</acronym>
  <official_title>Optimal Method of Decompression of the Renal Collecting System in Acute Obstruction: a Prospective Randomised Trial</official_title>
