  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Ureteric calculus with proximal hydronephrosis confirmed on CT KUB

          -  White cell count &gt;12,000mm3 and/or temperature &gt;38C

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Uncorrected coagulopathy

          -  Urethral or ureteric stricture disease

          -  Urinary diversion

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
